Q8. What makes a UI safe for AI workflows?
Ideal Answer:
“Clear workflow triggers, visibility on agent status, warnings for irreversible steps, 
input validation, error transparency, and audit-friendly logs.”
Q9. Securing a multi-system agent integration?
Ideal Answer:
“I’d use OAuth2 / RBAC, tool wrappers with strict validation, rate limits, retries with 
backoff, and full observability. Every tool call must be logged for traceability.”
Q10. RAG vs Fine-tuning?
Ideal Answer:
“Use RAG for dynamic knowledge and grounding; fine-tuning for behaviour 
consistency. In many enterprise cases, you start with RAG and add light fine-tuning 
for task style.”
